text:
Hi, today i cloned master branch and tried to start demo but gradle sync failed with this error:

Error:Could not find property 'bintray_user' on com.jfrog.bintray.gradle.BintrayExtension_Decorated@61eaae09.

have any suggestions how to resolve the issue ?
title: Gradle sync wont pass

text: Please wait, I'm finishing some clean up before final release so there may be some hidden flags ...

@andrijans @xylik At the mean time, please add the following to your ```gradle.properties``` file:

```groovy
bintray_user=
bintray_apikey=
bintray_gpg_password=
```

If empty string doesn't work, please add abitrary *one-character* Strings there (to prevent co-incident user/password, one-character is recommended since Bintray won't allow too short user name and password).
